    "note": "<div data-schema-version=\"9\"><p>The passages are from Great History and Doxography (Chos 'byung grub mtha' chen mo) by</p>\n<p>Rog Bande Sherab \u00d6 (1166-1244). For a biography of the author, see</p>\n<p>http://www.treasuryoflives.org/biographies/view/Rogben-Sherab-O/6726. The translation of the</p>\n<p>entire work is being published by Oxford under the title The Buddha's Doctrine and Nine</p>\n<p>Vehicles.</p>\n</div>",
